title: $:/plugins/rimir/cascade-palette/lens/modified
tags: $:/tags/rimir/cascade-palette/lens
ca-lens-name: Modified
ca-lens-chip: 🕒 Modified
ca-lens-hint: Trailing badge showing when each row's tiddler was last changed.
ca-lens-help: Projects the ANNOTATION slot (a trailing chip after the row name) with the row tiddler's last-modified date, formatted as "🕒 03rd Jun". A cheap FILTER projection (`ca-lens-annotation-filter`) — the common case for a computed string. Rows backed by no tiddler (transient filter results) get no chip. Data-model agnostic: works on any tiddler. Off by default.
ca-lens-annotation-filter: [<currentTiddler>get[modified]format:date[DDth MMM]addprefix[🕒 ]]
ca-order: 100
